# Plan Diagrams

This directory contains Mermaid diagram sources (.mmd) and generated images (.svg) for execution plans.

## Usage

- Place .mmd files here for plan visualizations
- Run diagram-to-image agent to convert to SVG
- Reference in plan markdown: `![Diagram](./diagrams/name.svg)`

## Naming Convention

- {slug}-{phase}-overview.mmd - Phase overview diagram
- {slug}-{phase}-components.mmd - Component interaction
- {slug}-{phase}-sequence.mmd - Sequence diagram

Example:
- auth-system-red-mock-setup.mmd
- auth-system-green-component-flow.mmd
